[
    {
        "index": 1,
        "start_time": 7124,
        "end_time": 11328,
        "text": "In 1997, \nin a game between France and Brazil,"
    },
    {
        "index": 2,
        "start_time": 11328,
        "end_time": 14387,
        "text": "a young Brazilian player\nnamed Roberto Carlos"
    },
    {
        "index": 3,
        "start_time": 14387,
        "end_time": 17502,
        "text": "set up for a 35 meter free kick."
    },
    {
        "index": 4,
        "start_time": 17502,
        "end_time": 19554,
        "text": "With no direct line to the goal,"
    },
    {
        "index": 5,
        "start_time": 19554,
        "end_time": 23859,
        "text": "Carlos decided to attempt \nthe seemingly impossible."
    },
    {
        "index": 6,
        "start_time": 23859,
        "end_time": 27068,
        "text": "His kick sent the ball flying\nwide of the players,"
    },
    {
        "index": 7,
        "start_time": 27068,
        "end_time": 30960,
        "text": "but just before going out of bounds,\nit hooked to the left"
    },
    {
        "index": 8,
        "start_time": 30960,
        "end_time": 33082,
        "text": "and soared into the goal."
    },
    {
        "index": 9,
        "start_time": 33082,
        "end_time": 35877,
        "text": "According to Newton&#39;s first law of motion,"
    },
    {
        "index": 10,
        "start_time": 35877,
        "end_time": 39246,
        "text": "an object will move \nin the same direction and velocity"
    },
    {
        "index": 11,
        "start_time": 39246,
        "end_time": 42077,
        "text": "until a force is applied on it."
    },
    {
        "index": 12,
        "start_time": 42077,
        "end_time": 45931,
        "text": "When Carlos kicked the ball,\nhe gave it direction and velocity,"
    },
    {
        "index": 13,
        "start_time": 45931,
        "end_time": 48696,
        "text": "but what force made the ball swerve"
    },
    {
        "index": 14,
        "start_time": 48696,
        "end_time": 53577,
        "text": "and score one of the most magnificent \ngoals in the history of the sport?"
    },
    {
        "index": 15,
        "start_time": 53577,
        "end_time": 55828,
        "text": "The trick was in the spin."
    },
    {
        "index": 16,
        "start_time": 55828,
        "end_time": 59515,
        "text": "Carlos placed his kick\nat the lower right corner of the ball,"
    },
    {
        "index": 17,
        "start_time": 59515,
        "end_time": 65142,
        "text": "sending it high and to the right,\nbut also rotating around its axis."
    },
    {
        "index": 18,
        "start_time": 65142,
        "end_time": 68223,
        "text": "The ball started its flight\nin an apparently direct route,"
    },
    {
        "index": 19,
        "start_time": 68223,
        "end_time": 72053,
        "text": "with air flowing on both sides\nand slowing it down."
    },
    {
        "index": 20,
        "start_time": 72053,
        "end_time": 76989,
        "text": "On one side, the air moved in the opposite\ndirection to the ball&#39;s spin,"
    },
    {
        "index": 21,
        "start_time": 76989,
        "end_time": 78890,
        "text": "causing increased pressure,"
    },
    {
        "index": 22,
        "start_time": 78890,
        "end_time": 83036,
        "text": "while on the other side, the air moved\nin the same direction as the spin,"
    },
    {
        "index": 23,
        "start_time": 83036,
        "end_time": 86114,
        "text": "creating an area of lower pressure."
    },
    {
        "index": 24,
        "start_time": 86114,
        "end_time": 90929,
        "text": "That difference made the ball curve\ntowards the lower pressure zone."
    },
    {
        "index": 25,
        "start_time": 90929,
        "end_time": 94302,
        "text": "This phenomenon is called\nthe Magnus effect."
    },
    {
        "index": 26,
        "start_time": 94302,
        "end_time": 97673,
        "text": "This type of kick, \noften referred to as a banana kick,"
    },
    {
        "index": 27,
        "start_time": 97673,
        "end_time": 99529,
        "text": "is attempted regularly,"
    },
    {
        "index": 28,
        "start_time": 99529,
        "end_time": 103581,
        "text": "and it is one of the elements\nthat makes the beautiful game beautiful."
    },
    {
        "index": 29,
        "start_time": 103581,
        "end_time": 105932,
        "text": "But curving the ball \nwith the precision needed"
    },
    {
        "index": 30,
        "start_time": 105932,
        "end_time": 111061,
        "text": "to both bend around the wall\nand back into the goal is difficult."
    },
    {
        "index": 31,
        "start_time": 111061,
        "end_time": 113314,
        "text": "Too high and it soars over the goal."
    },
    {
        "index": 32,
        "start_time": 113314,
        "end_time": 116587,
        "text": "Too low and it hits the ground \nbefore curving."
    },
    {
        "index": 33,
        "start_time": 116587,
        "end_time": 119093,
        "text": "Too wide and it never reaches the goal."
    },
    {
        "index": 34,
        "start_time": 119093,
        "end_time": 122591,
        "text": "Not wide enough \nand the defenders intercept it."
    },
    {
        "index": 35,
        "start_time": 122591,
        "end_time": 126068,
        "text": "Too slow and it hooks too early,\nor not at all."
    },
    {
        "index": 36,
        "start_time": 126068,
        "end_time": 129088,
        "text": "Too fast and it hooks too late."
    },
    {
        "index": 37,
        "start_time": 129088,
        "end_time": 130978,
        "text": "The same physics make it possible"
    },
    {
        "index": 38,
        "start_time": 130978,
        "end_time": 134386,
        "text": "to score another \napparently impossible goal,"
    },
    {
        "index": 39,
        "start_time": 134386,
        "end_time": 137504,
        "text": "an unassisted corner kick."
    },
    {
        "index": 40,
        "start_time": 137504,
        "end_time": 141032,
        "text": "The Magnus effect was first documented\nby Sir Isaac Newton"
    },
    {
        "index": 41,
        "start_time": 141032,
        "end_time": 146261,
        "text": "after he noticed it while playing a game\nof tennis back in 1670."
    },
    {
        "index": 42,
        "start_time": 146261,
        "end_time": 150217,
        "text": "It also applies to golf balls,\nfrisbees and baseballs."
    },
    {
        "index": 43,
        "start_time": 150217,
        "end_time": 153138,
        "text": "In every case, the same thing happens."
    },
    {
        "index": 44,
        "start_time": 153138,
        "end_time": 157634,
        "text": "The ball&#39;s spin creates a pressure \ndifferential in the surrounding air flow"
    },
    {
        "index": 45,
        "start_time": 157634,
        "end_time": 160651,
        "text": "that curves it \nin the direction of the spin."
    },
    {
        "index": 46,
        "start_time": 160651,
        "end_time": 161972,
        "text": "And here&#39;s a question."
    },
    {
        "index": 47,
        "start_time": 161972,
        "end_time": 164448,
        "text": "Could you theoretically \nkick a ball hard enough"
    },
    {
        "index": 48,
        "start_time": 164448,
        "end_time": 168292,
        "text": "to make it boomerang \nall the way around back to you?"
    },
    {
        "index": 49,
        "start_time": 168292,
        "end_time": 170139,
        "text": "Sadly, no."
    },
    {
        "index": 50,
        "start_time": 170139,
        "end_time": 172672,
        "text": "Even if the ball didn&#39;t \ndisintegrate on impact,"
    },
    {
        "index": 51,
        "start_time": 172672,
        "end_time": 174311,
        "text": "or hit any obstacles,"
    },
    {
        "index": 52,
        "start_time": 174311,
        "end_time": 175786,
        "text": "as the air slowed it,"
    },
    {
        "index": 53,
        "start_time": 175786,
        "end_time": 178897,
        "text": "the angle of its deflection \nwould increase,"
    },
    {
        "index": 54,
        "start_time": 178897,
        "end_time": 182658,
        "text": "causing it to spiral into smaller \nand smaller circles"
    },
    {
        "index": 55,
        "start_time": 182658,
        "end_time": 185287,
        "text": "until finally stopping."
    },
    {
        "index": 56,
        "start_time": 185287,
        "end_time": 187026,
        "text": "And just to get that spiral,"
    },
    {
        "index": 57,
        "start_time": 187026,
        "end_time": 191103,
        "text": "you&#39;d have to make the ball spin\nover 15 times faster"
    },
    {
        "index": 58,
        "start_time": 191103,
        "end_time": 193904,
        "text": "than Carlos&#39;s immortal kick."
    },
    {
        "index": 59,
        "start_time": 193904,
        "end_time": 196215,
        "text": "So good luck with that."
    }
]